source.query:
SELECT DISTINCT 
	TRIM(COALESCE(A.TERRITORY_ID,'')) AS "TERRITORY_ID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(C.TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "TERRITORY_NAME"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.NAME,'')) as "USER_NAME"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.EMAIL,'')) as "EMAIL"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.ALIAS_NAME,'')) as "MUDID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACTIVE_IND,'')) as "USR_TERR_ACTIVE_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.ACTIVE_IND,'')) as "USR_ACTIVE_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.DELETED_IND,'')) AS "USR_DELETED_ID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(A.USER_ID,'')) AS "USER_ID"
	,A.START_DATE as "START_DATE"
	,A.END_DATE (TITLE'') as "END_DATE"
 FROM 
	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.SCD_USER_TERRITORY A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER B
    	ON A.USER_ID = B.USER_ID
    LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_TERRITORY C
    ON	A.TERRITORY_ID = C.TERRITORY_ID;

SELECT DISTINCT
	TRIM(COALESCE(TR.FIELD_FORCE_NAME,'')) as "DIVISAO"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TE.TERRITORY_ID,'')) as "TERRITORY_ID"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TR.TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "TERRITORIO"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TE.LEVEL_4_TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "TERRITORIO_GD"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TE.LEVEL_5_TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "TERRITORIO_GR"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TE.LEVEL_6_TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "BU"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(TR.END_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),''))	(TITLE'') as "DATA_FIM_TERRITORIO"
 FROM   LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.SCD_HIERARCHY_TERRITORY TE LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_TERRITORY TR
		ON TE.TERRITORY_ID = TR.TERRITORY_ID
 WHERE 
	TE.DELETED_IND = 0 AND TE.CURRENT_IND = '1'
	AND EXISTS (SELECT A.* FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_TERRITORY A WHERE TE.TERRITORY_ID = A.TERRITORY_ID AND A.ACTIVE_IND = '1');

SELECT DISTINCT
     TRIM(SAMPLE_TRANSACTION_NAME)  as "ROW_ID"
     ,''                   as "EQUIPE"
     ,''                   as "REGIONAL"
     , TRIM(A.TERRITORY_ID)      as "SETOR"
     , TRIM(A.USER_ID)            as "USER_ID"
     , ''                   as "NUM_CRM"
     , TRIM(A.SIGNATURE_DATE_ID)       as "ASSINATURA"
     , ''                   as "NOME"
     , TRIM(A.CALL_NAME)          as "ID_VISITA"
     , TRIM(A.TRANSACTION_DATE_ID)     as "DATA_DA_VISITA"
     , TRIM(A.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID)  as "ID_MATERIAL_AMOSTRA"
     , TRIM(A.TRANSACTION_SAMPLE) as "AMOSTRA_MATERIAL_ME_MERCHANDISING"
     , TRIM(A.SAMPLE_LOT_ID)      as "LOTE"
     , TRIM(A.QUANTITY)     as "QUANTIDADE"
     , TRIM(A.ACCOUNT_ID)       as "PROF_ID" 
     , ''                   (TITLE'')       as "CATEGORIA"     
 FROM 
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SAMPLE_TRANSACTION A 
 WHERE 
     A.TYPE_CD = 'Disbursement_vod' AND 
     A.DELETED_IND = '0'
 AND
     
     ((SUBSTR(CAST(A.SUBMITTED_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.SUBMITTED_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (SUBSTR(CAST(A.SUBMITTED_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.SUBMITTED_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) ));

SELECT DISTINCT
	TRIM(TERRITORY_ID)	as "ROW_ID_TERRITORIO" 
	,TRIM(ACCOUNT_ID)	as "ROW_ID_CONTATO"
	,TRIM(ADDRESS_ID) as "ROW_ID_ENDERECO"	
	,TRIM(MY_TARGET_IND)	(TITLE'') as "TARGET_IND"
 FROM 
	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.H_TERR_SPECIFIC_FIELDS
 WHERE
     SOURCE_DELETED_IND = '0';

SELECT DISTINCT
     TRIM(COALESCE(A.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID,'')) as "ID_EVENTO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.LOCATION,'')) as "LOCALIZACAO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.EVENT_TYPE,''))  as "TIPO_EVENTO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(OREPLACE(A.EVENT_NAME,'~','-'),'')) as "NOME_EVENTO" 
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.START_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "DATA_INICIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.END_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "DATA_FIM"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(C.PRODUCT_NAME,'')) as "PRODUTO_PRIMARIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(D.PRODUCT_NAME,'')) as "PRODUTO_SECUNDARIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.TERRITORY_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_TERRITORIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_CONTATO" 
     , TRIM(COALESCE(E.RX_LEGAL_ID,'')) as "DOCUMENTO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_TYPE,'')) as "TIPO_CONTA"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.RX_ROLE,'')) as "TIPO_PARTICIPACAO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_STATUS,'')) "STATUS_CONVIDADO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(U.NAME,'')) as "CRIADO_POR"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(U.ALIAS_NAME,'')) as "CRIADO_POR_MUDID"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE,'')) (TITLE'') as "PARTICIPANTE"
          
 FROM 
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_MEDICAL_EVENT A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_MEDICAL_EVENT_ATTENDEE B
     ON A.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID = B.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG C
     ON A.RX_PRIMARY_PRODUCT = C.SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG D
     ON A.RX_SECONDARY_PRODUCT = D.SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ACCOUNT E
     ON B.ATTENDEE_ID = E.ACCOUNT_ID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER U
     ON A.OWNER_AID = U.SOURCE_USER_AID
     
 WHERE
     A.DELETED_IND = 0 AND B.DELETED_IND = 0
     AND
     ((EXTRACT(YEAR FROM END_DATE) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM END_DATE) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM END_DATE) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM END_DATE) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) )));

SELECT DISTINCT 
	TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACCOUNT_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_CONTATO"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.START_DATE_ID AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "START_DATE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_PRODUTO"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(B.PRODUCT_NAME,''))	as "PRODUCT_NAME"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.RX_ACTIVITY_END_TIME AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "END_DATE_TIME" 	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_ACTIVITY_TYPE,'')) as "ACTIVITY_TYPE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_ACTIVITY_OWNER,'')) 	as "ACTIVITY_OWNER"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_TRIGGER_SOURCE_TYPE,''))  as "TRIGGER_SOURCE_TYPE"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_DATASOURCE_CODE,'')) as "DATASOURCE_CODE"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.MC_ACTIVITY_NAME,''))		as "ACTIVITY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.URL,''))	(TITLE'') as "URL"
 FROM 
	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_MC_ACTIVITY A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG B
	ON	A.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID = B.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID
 WHERE
	A.DELETED_IND = '0';

SELECT DISTINCT 
	TRIM(COALESCE(TERRITORY_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_TERRITORIO"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(ACCOUNT_ID,'')) 	as "ROW_ID_CONTATO"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(ACCOUNT_ACCESS,''))  as "TIPO_ACESSO"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(ROW_CAUSE,''))	as "ROW_CAUSE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(SOURCE_DELETED_IND,''))	(TITLE'') as "DELETED_IND"
 FROM 
	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.V_ACCOUNT_TERRITORY
 WHERE
	SOURCE_DELETED_IND = '0'
	AND TERRITORY_ID <> '-1';

SELECT DISTINCT  
	TRIM(COALESCE(PRICING_BOUND_IND,''))  as "PRICING_BOUND_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(DELETED_IND,''))  as "DELETED_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(PRODUCT_NAME,''))  as "PRODUCT_NAME"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(PARENT_PRODUCT_AID,''))  as "PARENT_PRODUCT_AID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(INVENTORY_QUANTITY_PER_CASE,''))  as "INVENTORY_QUANTITY_PER_CASE"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(EXTERNAL_AID,''))  as "EXTERNAL_AID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(PRODUCT_TYPE,''))  as "PRODUCT_TYPE"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(COMPANY_PRODUCT_IND,''))  as "COMPANY_PRODUCT_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(CONSUMER_SITE,''))  as "CONSUMER_SITE"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(QUANTITY_PER_CASE,''))  as "QUANTITY_PER_CASE"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(CURRENCY_CODE,''))  as "CURRENCY_CODE"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(LAST_MODIFIED_DATE_TS AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "LAST_MODIFIED_DATE_TS"   
	,TRIM(COALESCE(COST,''))  as "COST"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(NO_METRICS_IND,'')) as "NO_METRIC_IND" 
	,TRIM(COALESCE(REQUIRE_KEY_MSG_ON_DTL_IND,''))  as "REQUIRE_KEY_MSG_ON_DTL_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(SAMPLE_QUANTITY_BOUND_IND,''))  as "SAMPLE_QUANTITY_BOUND_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(INSTANCE_ID,''))  as "INSTANCE_ID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(SCHEDULE,''))  as "SCHEDULE"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(SAMPLE_UOM,''))  as "SAMPLE_UOM"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(DISPLAY_ORDER,''))  as "DISPLAY_ORDER"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION,''))  as "PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID,''))  as "SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(COUNTRY_CODE,''))  as "COUNTRY_CODE"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(RESTRICTED_IND,''))  as "RESTRICTED_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(NO_CYCLE_PLANS_IND,''))  as "NO_CYCLE_PLANS_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(VEEVA_EXTERNAL_AID,''))  as "VEEVA_EXTERNAL_AID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(SORT_CODE,''))  as "SORT_CODE"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(THERAPEUTIC_AREA,''))  as "THERAPEUTIC_AREA"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(USER_ALIGNED_IND,''))  as "USER_ALIGNED_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(PRODUCT_INFO,''))  as "PRODUCT_INFO"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(LAST_MODIFIED_BY_AID,''))  as "LAST_MODIFIED_BY_AID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(THERAPEUTIC_CLASS,''))  as "THERAPEUTIC_CLASS"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(MANUFACTURER,''))  as "MANUFACTURER"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(LOCKED_IND,''))  as "LOCKED_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(CONTROLLED_SUBSTANCE_IND,''))   as "CONTROLLED_SUBSTANCE_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,''))  as "PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(RESTRICTED_STATES,'')) as "RESTRICTED_STATES"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(DISTRIBUTOR,''))  as "DISTRIBUTOR"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(PRICING_RULE_QTY_BOUND_IND,''))  as "PRICING_RULE_QTY_BOUND_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(BATCH_ID,''))  as "BATCH_ID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(OWNER_AID,'')) as "OWNER_AID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(RX_EXTERNAL_ID,''))  as "RX_EXTERNAL_ID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(NO_DETAILS_IND,''))  as "NO_DETAILS_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(INVENTORY_ORDER_UOM,''))  as "INVENTORY_ORDER_UOM"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(GSK_INACTIVE_IND,''))  (TITLE'')  as "GSK_INACTIVE_IND"
 FROM 
	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG;

SELECT DISTINCT 
     TRIM(COALESCE(B.SURVEY_TARGET_NAME,''))   as "NOME_SURVEY"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "DATA_CRIACAO"   
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS AS VARCHAR(100)),''))  as "DATA_MODIFICACAO" 
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ACCOUNT_ID,''))   as "ROW_ID_CONTATO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(D.ALIAS_NAME,''))   as "ROW_ID_TERRITORIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.QUESTION_ID,''))  as "ROW_ID_PERGUNTA" 
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE_NAME,''))   as "ROW_ID_RESPOSTA"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(E.QUESTION_TEXT,''))   as "PERGUNTA"
     , ''   as "PESO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE_NUMBER,'')) as "RESPOSTA_NUMERICA"   
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE,''))   as "RESPOSTA"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE_TEXT,''))   as "RESPOSTA_TEXTO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE_DECIMAL_VALUE,''))   as "RESPOSTA_DECIMAL"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.STATUS,''))  as "STATUS"
     , ''  as "RESPOSTA_FINAL"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.SURVEY_TARGET_ID,''))  (TITLE'') as "SURVEY_ID"
 FROM
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_TARGETS B
     ON   A.SURVEY_TARGET_ID = B.SURVEY_TARGET_ID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_SURVEY_QUESTION E
     ON   A.QUESTION_ID = E.QUESTION_ID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER D
     ON   A.SOURCE_CREATED_BY_AID = D.SOURCE_USER_AID
 WHERE
       
      ((EXTRACT(YEAR FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ))
     OR
     (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -2) )));

SELECT DISTINCT 
     TRIM(COALESCE(NAME,''))   as "ROW_ID"
     , ''    as "TERRITORIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(USER_ID,''))   as "ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(TERRITORY_ID,''))   AS "ROW_ID_POSICAO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(START_DATE_ID AS VARCHAR(100)),''))   as "DATATOT"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(REASON,''))   as "DESCRICAO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(HOURS,''))  (TITLE'') as "TEMPO"
 FROM 
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_TIME_OFF_TERRITORY
 WHERE
     DELETED_IND = 0 AND
     
     ((SUBSTR(CAST(START_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(START_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (SUBSTR(CAST(START_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(START_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) )));

SELECT DISTINCT
     TRIM(COALESCE(A.DELETED_IND,'')) as "DELETED_IND"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.CALL_STATUS,'')) as "CALL_STATUS"
     ,''   as "TERRITORIO"
     ,''   as "ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.TERRITORY_ID,''))  as "ROW_ID_POSICAO"   
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.CALL_NAME,''))   as "ACTIVITY_UID"    
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.ATTENDEE_TYPE,''))    as "TIPO"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID,''))  as "TODO_PLAN_START_DT"  
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.LOCAL_CALL_TIME_ID,''))  as  "HORA"
     ,''   as "NOMECONTATOCONTA"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.OWNER_ID,'')) as "OWNER_PER_ID"   
     ,''  as "OWNER_POSTN_ID"
     ,''   as "DIVISAO"
     ,''   as "ROW_ID_DIVISAO"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.CALL_TYPE,'')) as "TODO_CD"       
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACCOUNT_ID,'')) as "TARGET_PER_ID"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_CALL_TYPE,''))  as "TARGET_OU_ID"   
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.DETAILED_PRODUCTS,'')) as "COMENTARIOS"
     ,''   as "UFDOCUMENTO"
     ,''   as "NUMERODOCUMENTO"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(B.ADDRESS_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_ENDERECO" 
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.CLM_IND,''))    as "CLM_IND"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.NEXT_CALL_NOTES,'')) as "NEXT_CALL_NOTES"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(A.RECORD_TYPE_ID,'')) as "RECORD_TYPE_ID"
     ,TRIM(COALESCE(R.RECORD_TYPE_NAME,'')) (TITLE'') as "RECORD_TYPE_NAME"
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ADDRESS B
          ON A.PARENT_ADDRESS_ID = B.ADDRESS_ID,
      LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_RECORD_TYPE R
 WHERE
     A.CALL_STATUS = 'Submitted_vod' AND
     A.DELETED_IND = 0 AND
     
     ((SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) )))
     
     AND (A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Detail' AND A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Only' AND A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Sample Only' AND A.CALL_TYPE <> oreplace('Item drop#only', '#', ' '))
     AND A.PARENT_CALL_AID IS NULL
     AND  A.RECORD_TYPE_ID = R.RECORD_TYPE_ID;

SELECT DISTINCT 
			TRIM(COALESCE(E.CALL_SUMMARY_ID,'')) as "CALL_SUMMARY_ID"
           , TRIM(COALESCE(D.KEY_MESSAGE_ID,'')) as "KEY_MESSAGE_ID"
	        , TRIM(COALESCE(D.CATEGORY,'')) as "CATEGORY"
	        , TRIM(COALESCE(CASE WHEN (D.KEY_MESSAGE_NAME IN ('QUALIFICAO','QUALIFICA?O')) THEN ('QUALIFICACAO') 
	                 WHEN (D.KEY_MESSAGE_NAME IN ('PROSPECO','PROSPEC?O')) THEN ('PROSPECCAO') ELSE D.KEY_MESSAGE_NAME END,'')) as "KEY_MESSAGE_NAME"
	        , TRIM(COALESCE(E.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,'')) (TITLE'') as "PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID"
  FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_MESSAGE E LEFT OUTER JOIN
                 LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_KEY_MESSAGE D    
              ON E.KEY_MESSAGE_ID = D.KEY_MESSAGE_ID 
  WHERE D.CATEGORY = 'Key Message';

SELECT DISTINCT TRIM(COALESCE(A.CALL_SUMMARY_ID,'')) as "CALL_SUMMARY_ID"
                , TRIM(COALESCE(B.CALL_NAME,'')) as "CALL_NAME"
                , TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACCOUNT_ID,'')) as "ACCOUNT_ID"
                , TRIM(COALESCE(A.TERRITORY_ID,'')) as "TERRITORY_ID"
                , TRIM(COALESCE(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID,'')) as "LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID"
             , TRIM(COALESCE(A.SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID,'')) (TITLE'')  as "SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID"          
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY A INNER JOIN
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY B
   ON A.PARENT_CALL_AID = B.SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID 
 WHERE A.PARENT_CALL_AID IS NOT NULL AND

 ((SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) )))

 AND (A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Detail' AND A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Only' AND A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Sample Only');

SELECT DISTINCT 
				TRIM(COALESCE(A.CALL_SUMMARY_ID,'')) as "CALL_SUMMARY_ID"
                , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ACCOUNT_ID,'')) (TITLE'')     as "ACCOUNT_ID"       
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY A INNER JOIN
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY B
   ON A.PARENT_CALL_AID = B.SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID 
 WHERE A.PARENT_CALL_AID IS NOT NULL AND

 (SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ))

 AND (A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Detail' AND A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Only' AND A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Sample Only');

SELECT DISTINCT 
				TRIM(COALESCE(A.CALL_SUMMARY_ID,'')) as "CALL_SUMMARY_ID"
                , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ACCOUNT_ID,'')) (TITLE'')     as "ACCOUNT_ID"       
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY A INNER JOIN
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY B
   ON A.PARENT_CALL_AID = B.SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID 
 WHERE A.PARENT_CALL_AID IS NOT NULL AND

 (SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ))

 AND (A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Detail' AND A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Only' AND A.CALL_TYPE <> 'Sample Only');

SELECT DISTINCT
       TRIM(COALESCE(TERRITORY_ID,''))  as "TERRITORY_ID"                
       , TRIM(COALESCE(ACCOUNT_ID,''))  as   "ACCOUNT_ID"                
       , TRIM(COALESCE(BR_GSK_MY_SPECIALTY,''))   as "BR_GSK_MY_SPECIALTY"       
       , TRIM(COALESCE(ADDRESS_ID,'')) as "ADDRESS_ID"                  
       , TRIM(COALESCE(oreplace(TSF_NAME,'BR_',''),'')) (TITLE'')  as "TSF_NAME"
 FROM 
            LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.H_TERR_SPECIFIC_FIELDS
 WHERE  
SOURCE_DELETED_IND = '0' AND    BR_GSK_MY_SPECIALTY IS NOT NULL;

SELECT DISTINCT
     TRIM(COALESCE(A.EMAIL_ACTIVITY_ID,'')) as "EMAIL_ACTIVITY_ID"    
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.SEND_EMAIL_ID,''))   as "SEND_EMAIL_ID"     
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.EMAIL_ACTIVITY_NAME,''))   as "EMAIL_ACTIVITY_NAME"    
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACTIVITY_DATE_ID,''))  as "ACTIVITY_DATE_ID"      
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACTIVITY_TIME_ID,''))  as "ACTIVITY_TIME_ID"     
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.LOCAL_ACTIVITY_DATE_ID,''))  as "LOCAL_ACTIVITY_DATE_ID"     
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.LOCAL_ACTIVITY_TIME_ID,'')) as "LOCAL_ACTIVITY_TIME_ID"      
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.OWNER_ID,''))  as "OWNER_ID"      
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACCOUNT_ID,''))    as "ACCOUNT_ID"    
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID,''))  as "BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID"     
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,''))   as "PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID"     
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.TERRITORY_ID,''))    as "TERRITORY_ID"    
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.EVENT_TYPE,''))   as "EVENT_TYPE"     
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.DEVICE_TYPE,''))  as "DEVICE_TYPE"      
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.CLICK_URL,''))    as "CLICK_URL"    
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.APPROVED_DOCUMENT_ID,''))  as "APPROVED_DOCUMENT_ID"       
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.APPROVED_DOCUMENT_NAME,'')) as "APPROVED_DOCUMENT_NAME"       
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.DOCUMENT_DESCRIPTION,'')) as "DOCUMENT_DESCRIPTION"        
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.EMAIL_SUBJECT,'')) (TITLE'') as "EMAIL_SUBJECT"
     
 FROM 
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_EMAIL_ACTIVITY A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_APPROVED_DOCUMENT B
     ON A.APPROVED_DOCUMENT_ID = B.APPROVED_DOCUMENT_ID
 WHERE 
     A.DELETED_IND = '0' AND

     ((SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_ACTIVITY_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_ACTIVITY_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_ACTIVITY_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.LOCAL_ACTIVITY_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) )));

SELECT DISTINCT 
	TRIM(COALESCE(A.SAMPLE_LOT_ID,'')) as "SAMPLE_LOT_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.DELETED_IND,'')) as "DELETED_IND"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.SOURCE_SAMPLE_LOT_AID,'')) as "SOURCE_SAMPLE_LOT_AID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_EXTERNAL_SAMPLE_LOT_AID,'')) as "RX_EXTERNAL_SAMPLE_LOT_AID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.SAMPLE_NAME,'')) as "SAMPLE_NAME"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(B.ALIAS_NAME,'')) (TITLE'') as "ALIAS_NAME"
 FROM 
	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_SAMPLE_LOT A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER B
	ON A.OWNER_AID = B.SOURCE_USER_AID;

SELECT DISTINCT
	TRIM(COALESCE(A.MC_CONSENT_ID,'')) 					as "MC_CONSENT_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.EXTERNAL_AID,''))                   as "EXTERNAL_AID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.SOURCE_MC_CONSENT_AID,''))          as "SOURCE_MC_CONSENT_AID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.INSTANCE_ID,''))                    as "INSTANCE_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.BATCH_ID,''))                       as "BATCH_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.PAPER_CONSENT_AID,''))              as "PAPER_CONSENT_AID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.CAPTURE_DATE_ID,''))                as "CAPTURE_DATE_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.DETAIL_GROUP_ID,''))                as "DETAIL_GROUP_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACCOUNT_ID,''))                     as "ACCOUNT_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,''))             as "PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.TERRITORY_ID,''))                   as "TERRITORY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RECORD_TYPE_ID,''))                 as "RECORD_TYPE_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.CAPTURE_TIME_ID,''))                as "CAPTURE_TIME_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.EXPIRATION_DATE_ID,''))             as "EXPIRATION_DATE_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.SIGNATURE_DATETIME_ID,''))          as "SIGNATURE_DATETIME_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_ID,''))           as "PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.PRODUCT_DEFINED_HIERARCHY_ID,''))   as "PRODUCT_DEFINED_HIERARCHY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.TERRITORY_HIERARCHY_ID,''))         as "TERRITORY_HIERARCHY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.CHANNEL_VALUE,''))                  as "CHANNEL_VALUE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.OPTION_NUMBER,''))                  as "OPTION_NUMBER"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.OPTION_TYPE,''))                    as "OPTION_TYPE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.EVENT_TYPE,''))                     as "EVENT_TYPE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.DELETED_IND,''))                    as "DELETED_IND"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.USER_TERRITORY_HELPER_ID,''))       as "USER_TERRITORY_HELPER_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.SCD_ACCOUNT_PERSONA_ID,''))         as "SCD_ACCOUNT_PERSONA_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.SCD_ACCOUNT_SPECIALTY_ID,''))       as "SCD_ACCOUNT_SPECIALTY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.SCD_ACCOUNT_SEGMENT_ID,''))         as "SCD_ACCOUNT_SEGMENT_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.SCD_ACCOUNT_CUSTOMER_JOURNEY_ID,'')) as "SCD_ACCOUNT_CUSTOMER_JOURNEY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.TERRITORY_DEFINED_HIERARCHY_ID,'')) as "TERRITORY_DEFINED_HIERARCHY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.COUNTRY_ID,''))                     as "COUNTRY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.COUNTRY_CODE,''))	(TITLE'')       as "COUNTRY_CODE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(B.RECORD_TYPE_NAME,'')) AS "RECORD_TYPE_NAME"
 FROM	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_MC_CONSENT A
	LEFT JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_RECORD_TYPE as B ON A.RECORD_TYPE_ID = B.RECORD_TYPE_ID
 WHERE
	A.DELETED_IND = '0';

SELECT DISTINCT 
    TRIM(B.CALL_NAME)        as "CALL_NAME" 
    , TRIM(A.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID)      as "LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID"
    , TRIM(A.LOCAL_CALL_TIME_ID)      as "LOCAL_CALL_TIME_ID"
    , TRIM(A.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID)      as "PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID"
    , TRIM(A.DETAIL_TYPE)        as "DETAIL_TYPE"
    , TRIM(A.CALL_TYPE)          as "CALL_TYPE"
    , TRIM(A.PRIORITY) (TITLE'') as "PRIORITY"
 FROM 
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_DETAIL A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY B
    ON   A.SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID = B.SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID
 WHERE
    EXISTS (SELECT C.SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID 
                FROM 
                     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY C
               WHERE
                    A.SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID = C.SOURCE_CALL_SUMMARY_AID AND
                    C.CALL_STATUS = 'Submitted_vod' AND
                     C.DELETED_IND = 0 AND
                     
                     ((SUBSTR(CAST(C.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
                      SUBSTR(CAST(C.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
                     OR
                     (SUBSTR(CAST(C.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
                      SUBSTR(CAST(C.LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) )))
                     
                     AND (C.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Detail' AND C.CALL_TYPE <> 'Event Only' AND C.CALL_TYPE <> 'Sample Only' AND C.CALL_TYPE <> oReplace('Item drop#only', '#', ' '))
                     AND C.PARENT_CALL_AID IS NULL);

SELECT DISTINCT
     TRIM(COALESCE(A.SOURCE_MC_CYCLE_PLAN_AID,'')) 					as "SOURCE_MC_CYCLE_PLAN_AID"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(C.USER_ID,''))                                 as "USER_ID"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.START_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),''))        as "START_DATE"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.END_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),''))          as "END_DATE"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.CHANNEL_INTERACTIONS_GOAL,''))               as "CHANNEL_INTERACTIONS_GOAL_CYCLE"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.DAYS_REMAINING,''))                          as "DAYS_REMAINING"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.DAYS_TOTAL,''))                              as "DAYS_TOTAL"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.CYCLE_PLAN_NAME,''))                         as "CYCLE_PLAN_NAME"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.CYCLE_COMPLETED_PERCENTAGE,''))              as "CYCLE_COMPLETED_PERCENTAGE"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.PRODUCT_INTERACTION_STATUS,''))              as "PRODUCT_INTERACTION_STATUS"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.PRODUCT_INTERACTIONS_GOAL,''))               as "PRODUCT_INTERACTIONS_GOAL_CYLE"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RECORD_TYPE,''))                             as "RECORD_TYPE"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.STATUS,''))                                  as "STATUS_CYCLE"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.TERRITORY,''))                               as "TERRITORY"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.MC_CYCLE_AID,''))                            as "MC_CYCLE_AID"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.MC_CYCLE_PLAN_TARGET_ID,''))                 as "MC_CYCLE_PLAN_TARGET_ID"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.SRC_MY_CYCLE_PLAN_TARGET_AID,''))            as "SRC_MY_CYCLE_PLAN_TARGET_AID"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.CYCLE_PLAN_TARGET_NAME,''))                  as "CYCLE_PLAN_TARGET_NAME"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.CHANNEL_INTERACTIONS_ACTUAL,''))             as "CHANNEL_INTERACTIONS_ACTUAL"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.CHANNEL_INTERACTIONS_GOAL,''))               as "CHANNEL_INTERACTIONS_GOAL"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.CHANNEL_INTERACTIONS_REMAINING,''))          as "CHANNEL_INTERACTIONS_REMAINING"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.PRODUCT_INTERACTIONS_GOAL,''))               as "PRODUCT_INTERACTIONS_GOAL"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.CHANNEL_STATUS,''))                          as "CHANNEL_STATUS"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.PRODUCT_STATUS,''))                          as "PRODUCT_STATUS"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.STATUS,''))                                  as "STATUS"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ACCOUNT_AID,''))                             as "ACCOUNT_AID"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(B.CREATED_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),''))      as "CREATED_DATE"     
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(B.LAST_MODIFIED_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) (TITLE'') as "LAST_MODIFIED_DATE"
 FROM
  LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_MC_CYCLE_PLAN A
  LEFT OUTER JOIN (
               SELECT *
               FROM
                     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_MC_CYCLE_PLAN_TARGET
               WHERE
                    DELETED_IND = '0' OR (DELETED_IND = '1' AND ARCHIVED_IND = '1')) B
 ON A.SOURCE_MC_CYCLE_PLAN_AID = B.MC_CYCLE_PLAN_AID
          LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER C
  ON                 A.OWNER_AID = C.SOURCE_USER_AID
 WHERE
 (A.DELETED_IND = 0 OR (A.DELETED_IND = '1' AND A.ARCHIVED_IND = '1'))
 AND 

     ((SUBSTR(CAST(A.START_DATE as VARCHAR(10)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.START_DATE as VARCHAR(10)),6,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (SUBSTR(CAST(A.START_DATE as VARCHAR(10)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.START_DATE as VARCHAR(10)),6,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) )));

SELECT DISTINCT
	TRIM(COALESCE(DELETED_IND,'')) 						AS "DELETED_IND"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(INACTIVE_IND,''))					AS "INACTIVE_IND"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(ACCOUNT_AID,''))                    AS "ROW_ID_CONTATO_EXT"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(ADDRESS_LINE_1,''))                 AS "LOGRADOURO"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(ADDRESS_ID,''))                     AS "ROW_ID_ENDERECO"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(CUSTOMER_MASTER_STATUS,''))         AS "STATUS_ENDERECO"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(RX_TYPE,''))                        AS "TIPO"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(ADDRESS_LINE_2,''))                 AS "BAIRRO"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(CITY,''))                           AS "CIDADE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(ZIP,''))                            AS "CEP"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(PRIMARY_ADDRESS_IND,''))            AS "ENDERECO_PRIMARIO"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(STATE,''))                          AS "UF"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(PHONE,''))                          AS "TELEFONE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(PHONE_2,''))                        AS "TELEFONE2"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(SOURCE_ADDRESS_AID,'')) (TITLE'')   AS "ROW_ID_END_EXT"
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ADDRESS;

SELECT
      MIN(J.CUSTOMER_JOURNEY) as "CUSTOMER_JOURNEY"
      , CASE MIN(J.CUSTOMER_JOURNEY)
        WHEN 'Reach' THEN 'COMPREENSO'
        WHEN 'Acquisition' THEN 'EXPERIMENTAO'
        WHEN 'Conversion' THEN 'EXPANSO'
        WHEN 'Engagement' THEN 'ADESO'
  END as "JORNADA"
      , P.PRODUCT_NAME  as "PRODUTO"
      , A.RX_LEGAL_ID as "DOCUMENTO"
      , A.ID_2 as "LEGAL_ID_2"
      , A.RX_LEGACY_ID as "RX_LEGACY_ID" 
      , FIRST_NAME || ' ' || MIDDLE_NAME || ' ' || LAST_NAME as "NOME_REPRESENTANTE"
      , A.ACCOUNT_ID as "ROW_ID_CONTATO"
      , A.RX_NETWORK_AID as "NETWORKID"
      , A.RX_ACCOUNT_VEEVA_ID as "ROW_ID_CONTATO_EXT"
      , J.START_DATE as "DT_INICIO_VEEVA"
      , CURRENT_DATE as "DT_INCLUSAO"
   FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.S_CUSTOMER_JOURNEY J
      LEFT JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ACCOUNT A ON (A.ACCOUNT_ID = J.ACCOUNT_ID)
      LEFT JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG P ON (P.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID = J.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID)
      LEFT JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_COUNTRY C ON (C.COUNTRY_ID = J.COUNTRY_ID)
   WHERE CURRENT_DATE BETWEEN START_DATE AND END_DATE 
      AND C.COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR'
      AND CUSTOMER_JOURNEY <> 'UNSPECIFIED' 
      AND A.RX_ACCOUNT_VEEVA_ID IS NOT NULL
      AND P.COMPANY_PRODUCT_IND = '1' 
      AND P.PRODUCT_NAME IN ('BEXSERO', 'BENLYSTA', 'NUCALA', 'TIVICAY', 'NUCALA GEPA')
   GROUP BY  
      P.PRODUCT_NAME,
      A.RX_LEGAL_ID,
      A.ID_2, 
      A.RX_LEGACY_ID,
      START_DATE, 
      FIRST_NAME || ' ' || MIDDLE_NAME || ' ' || LAST_NAME,
      A.ACCOUNT_ID, 
      A.RX_NETWORK_AID, 
      A.RX_ACCOUNT_VEEVA_ID 
   ORDER BY START_DATE DESC;

select *  
    FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_EM_EVENT;

SELECT DISTINCT 
                TRIM(COALESCE(A.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID,''))                  AS "ID_EVENTO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(A.LOCATION,''))                          AS "LOCALIZACAO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(A.EVENT_TYPE,''))                        AS "TIPO_EVENTO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(OREPLACE(A.EVENT_NAME,'~','-'),''))      AS "NOME_EVENTO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.START_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),''))  AS "DATA_INICIO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.END_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),''))    AS "DATA_FIM",
                TRIM(COALESCE(C.PRODUCT_NAME,''))                      AS "PRODUTO_PRIMARIO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(D.PRODUCT_NAME,''))                      AS "PRODUTO_SECUNDARIO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.TERRITORY_ID,''))                      AS "ROW_ID_TERRITORIO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_ID,''))                       AS "ROW_ID_CONTATO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(E.RX_LEGAL_ID,''))                       AS "DOCUMENTO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_TYPE,''))                     AS "TIPO_CONTA",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.RX_ROLE,''))                           AS "TIPO_PARTICIPACAO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_STATUS,''))                   AS "STATUS_CONVIDADO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(U.NAME,''))                              AS "CRIADO_POR",
                TRIM(COALESCE(U.ALIAS_NAME,''))                        AS "CRIADO_POR_MUDID",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE,''))                          AS "PARTICIPANTE",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.RX_ATTENDEE_SPECIALTY,''))             AS "ESPECIALIDADE" 
                               
    FROM  
                LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_MEDICAL_EVENT A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_MEDICAL_EVENT_ATTENDEE B
                ON A.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID = B.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID
                
                LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG C
                ON A.RX_PRIMARY_PRODUCT = C.SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID
                
                LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG D
                ON A.RX_SECONDARY_PRODUCT = D.SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID
                
                LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ACCOUNT E
                ON B.ATTENDEE_ID = E.ACCOUNT_ID
                
                LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER U
                ON A.OWNER_AID = U.SOURCE_USER_AID
                
    WHERE  
       A.DELETED_IND = 0 AND B.DELETED_IND = 0
       AND
          EXTRACT(YEAR FROM END_DATE) >= EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -8)) 
       AND
          EXTRACT(MONTH FROM END_DATE) >= EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -8));
